..TEXT:
|domandal~ = ^domandalo~ (pronounced ^dom@andalo~).
The accusative for the person interrogated is commonly used with
the verb ^domandare~ in early Italian.  |che pi@u li t'avvicini~
= ^che pi@u gli sei vicino.~
