..TEXT:
|a man dritta~: Dante was facing Sapia as he spoke
with her and so was facing the bank of the terrace.  The souls
are seated in single file along the base of the bank, and the two
souls who speak now are therefore to the right of anyone facing
the bank.  Dante continues to move in the proper direction for
Purgatory.
