..TEXT:
|onde vieni e chi se'~: Again, as with Sapia, the
first question concerns one's place of origin, the second, one's
name.  Compare Dante's words to Sapia in ^Purg.~ XIII, 105: "o
per luogo o per nome."  Dante will answer both questions in the
two tercets that follow.  |ne~ = ^ci.~
