..TEXT:
|che 'l nome di tal valle p@era~: See Iob 18:17:
"Memoria illius pereat de terra."  ("His memory perishes from the
land.")  The "valle" is, of course, the Val d'Arno, which
together with the river itself becomes the subject of the long
discourse which follows.  |p@era~ = ^perisca.~
