..TEXT:
|dirizza prima il suo povero calle~: The river sets
out, as it were, on its way, which is termed "poor" for the same
reason that the river itself was called a "stream" at the
beginning (see n. to vs. 17).  The personification of the river,
clearly suggested before, is now explicit and will remain so.
