|buon sar@a.~..^disnoda~: It will be good for
this Tuscan (the speaker does not know who Dante is) to bear in
mind (^ammentarsi~) when he returns to the world of the living
(^ancor~) what I am about to say prophetically, since this
concerns grievous things for the city of Florence.
