|le donne e ' cavalier...cortesia~: "Le donne
e ' cavalier" and "li affanni e li agi" constitute the object of
the verb, the dual subject of which is "amore e cortesia." |109.
li affanni e li agi~: The labors (military exploits) and the
pastimes.  The pair of terms corresponds to the "vero" and
"trastullo" of vs. 93.
